| Purpose                | Color Code | Notes                           |
| ---------------------- | ---------- | ------------------------------- |
| **Primary Blue**       | `#1E88E5`  | Main buttons, headers           |
| **Light Blue**         | `#E3F2FD`  | Background highlights, sections |
| **Accent Blue**        | `#1565C0`  | Hover states, links             |
| **White**              | `#FFFFFF`  | Main background                 |
| **Gray (Text)**        | `#444444`  | Primary text color              |
| **Light Gray Border**  | `#DDDDDD`  | Field borders or dividers       |
| **Success (Optional)** | `#4CAF50`  | For success notifications       |
| **Error (Optional)**   | `#E53935`  | For error messages              |
